T Boots, J Boots, or Sow Potions<br>
Level 54 Water Rogue Pet<br>
Level 53 Necromancer Parter with Level 53 Skeleton Pet<br>
<br>
Technique:<br>
1.) Buff pets (Burnout/Augment, Expedience, Fireshield)<br>
2.) Necromancer uses Lich to convert his HPs to Mana<br>
3.) Mage pulls with summoned daggers while necromancer meditates<br>
4.) Necromancer uses snare (cascading darkness)<br>
5.) Necromancer uses fear<br>
6.) Both pets backstab<br>
7.) Necromancer uses lifetap to get hps back<br>
8.) DD as necessary (not very hehe)<br>
9.) Repeat<br>
<br>
I didn't cast much except to put fireshield on pets and the occasional shield or pet buff refresh.  I also medded sometimes during the pets melee while they were running fast with expedience after the feared mobs.  DD only as necessary.<br>
<br>
I did something like this in BW with ZERO downtime.  It was great.<br>
<br>
Try it sometime.<br>
<br>
